I genuinely have no idea how people get to more than 100 hours on this game and still have their computer alive and well, when i say this i mean that ark is the only game to ever literally overheat my cpu (ryzen 9 5900HX btw) and trigger the restart failsafe for the computer to not just die. i DO like the game and i DO want to play it, its just that i literally cant do that without my entire pc possibly becoming an electric grill. i would recommend if you have THE BEST cooling system in the world, but any other than that will simply not do (yes i do have a really good cooling pad for my laptop, this still happens).
if you are not careful, this game WILL kill your computer. (not saying from experience)

all in all, this a good game until it comes to bugs and optimization, i will not talk about bugs but ark is the MOST UN-OPTIMIZED game i have EVER seen, NO game has been able to cook my cpu as good as ark. i have heard that the epic games version of ark doesnt kill your pc, so if you want ark, go there.

ark is kind of a mess, for one it's buggy as hell, sometimes whenever I try to log on it just doesn't. Another BIG problem is that they keep adding op dinosaurs which allow alpha tribes to wipe all small and/or casual tribes from the face of earth.

in summary ;
shit game do not buy.
